 \mbox{Let's}\quad r \equiv {x \over x + y}\quad\mbox{such that}\quad {4xy \over \pars{x + y}^{2}} = 4r\pars{1 - r} =1 - \pars{2r - 1}^{2} \leq 1 
\ds{\sec^{2}\pars{\theta} \geq 1}
